      <h2>Symptom Checker Tips</h2>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Be Specific</h3>
          <p>Describe your symptoms in detail for more accurate advice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Track Duration</h3>
          <p>Note how long you have had each symptom and if it is getting better or worse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>List All Symptoms</h3>
          <p>Mention all symptoms, even if they seem unrelated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Seek Help</h3>
          <p>If symptoms are severe or worsening, contact a healthcare provider immediately.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Is this a diagnosis?</h3>
          <p>No, this tool provides guidance but does not replace a professional diagnosis.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>What if I have an emergency?</h3>
          <p>Call emergency services or go to the nearest hospital immediately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Can I use this for children?</h3>
          <p>Yes, but always consult a doctor for children with serious symptoms.</p>
        </div>
